**Version:** 1.0
**Date:** 2026-05-16
**Owner:** Viktor AI + Codex
**App:** `course-swipefile-manager` → upgraded to **Course Intelligence Directory**
**Convex URL:** `https://giant-lyrebird-497.convex.cloud`
**Production URL:** `command.insightprofit.live` (integrated)

---

## 1. Executive Summary

Transform the existing `course-swipefile-manager` Viktor Space (433 courses, basic CRUD) into a full **visual intelligence directory** with:
- Auto-captured sales page screenshots as thumbnails
- AI-powered categorization and tagging
- Deep multi-faceted filtering (bundle, category, creator, tags, price, format, status)
- Visual card grid + PowerTable + group-by views
- Custom collections (mix-and-match across bundles)
- AI content engine: generate lead magnets, emails, social posts from course content
- Course file indexer: scan MEGA/Drive folder structures
- Natural language semantic search
- Video intelligence via Gemini 3 Pro (Phase 3)

---

## 2. Current State Analysis

### 2.1 Data in Convex DB (433 courses, 10 bundles)
| Field | Coverage | Notes |
|-------|----------|-------|
| courseName | 433/433 ✅ | Full coverage |
| salesPage | 431/433 ✅ | Almost all have URLs |
| creator | 433/433 ✅ | Extracted from course name |
| description | 192/433 | ~44% have descriptions |
| megaFolder | 17/433 | Only Diamond + Killer bundles |
| googleDrive | 20/433 | Only Diamond + Killer bundles |
| thumbnail | 0/433 ❌ | None captured yet |
| tags | 0/433 ❌ | No tagging system |
| category | 0/433 ❌ | All "Uncategorized" |
| price | varies | Some have prices |

### 2.2 Google Sheet Source
- **Sheet ID:** `1d1i52mxGF8dzusw_9bc2uIvJrLrrCJ1JBAWbk8ouvSM`
- **Title:** "WSO Pros Monster Group Buy - Course Details"
- **13 tabs:** Sheet1 (84), Maria Wendt (45), Diamond Group Buy (6), XXX (74), Monster (55), 8 (82), 5 (64), + 6 empty tabs
- **~410 total rows** with rich data including:
  - Course Name, Title, Description, Creator, Sales Page, Category, Price
  - Full Page Content Text (scraped sales copy)
  - Download Links, Quality flags, Course Type
  - Course Thumbnail, Sales Page Preview (column headers exist but mostly empty)

### 2.3 Existing App Architecture
- **Stack:** React 19 + Convex + Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui + Vite
- **Auth:** Convex Auth (email/password)
- **Backend:** Full CRUD, search index, bulk operations
- **Frontend:** 5 pages (Dashboard, Landing, Login, Signup, Settings)
- **Components:** SwipefileManager, BundleSelector, CategoryFilter, CourseTable, CreativeStudio, ManagePanel
- **Viktor Tools:** quickAiSearch, generateImage already wired

