| `courses:batchCaptureScreenshots` | Process all courses without screenshots |
| `courses:enrichWithAI` | Generate AI summary + content DNA for a course |
| `courses:batchEnrich` | Batch AI enrichment |
| `collections:create` | Create custom collection |
| `collections:addCourses` | Add courses to collection |
| `generatedContent:generateFromCourse` | AI content generator |
| `aiJobs:create` | Create and track AI job progress |

