| Task | Tokens | Cost | Notes |
|------|--------|------|-------|
| Categorize 433 courses | ~650K tokens | ~$0.65 | GPT-4o-mini at $0.10/100K |
| Tag 433 courses | ~650K tokens | ~$0.65 | Same model |
