| Whisper transcription | ~$15 | $0.006/min × 50 hours |
| **Phase 3 Total** | **~$45** | |

### 5.5 Total Cost

| Phase | One-Time | Monthly |
|-------|----------|---------|
| Phase 1 | ~$5 | $0-25 |
| Phase 2 | ~$3 | ~$1 |
| Phase 3 | ~$45 | ~$5 |
| **Grand Total** | **~$53** | **$1-31/mo** |

**vs. comparable SaaS:** Airtable + Notion + Algolia + custom dev = $500-2,000/mo

