## 12. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Sales page URLs broken (404) | Fallback to placeholder thumbnail + store URL status |
| Convex free tier exceeded | Batch screenshots, lazy-load images, use CDN URLs |
| AI categorization wrong | Manual override + re-categorize button per course |
| Google Sheet format changes | Flexible column mapping, log mismatches |
| Large dataset performance | Paginate all queries (50 per page), virtual scroll |
| Screenshot capture blocked | Retry with different browser user-agent, use cached versions |
